import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import ListGroup from 'react-bootstrap/ListGroup';
import Button from "react-bootstrap/Button";


const Dish = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://www.themealdb.com/images/media/meals/va668f1683209318.jpg" />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>Tortang Talong</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>address</Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
        <ListGroup className="list-group-flush">
          <ListGroup.Item>Comment 1</ListGroup.Item>
          <ListGroup.Item>Comment 2</ListGroup.Item>
          <ListGroup.Item>Comment 3</ListGroup.Item>
        </ListGroup>
        <Card.Body>
        <Button variant="outline-success">Comment</Button>
        <Button variant="outline-success">Save</Button>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
        </>
    )
}

export default Dish
